		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/IntuitiveWebsites-CoolSitesHotReturns/~3/cFK9HU8Y7TA/</link>
		<comments>http://www.intuitiveblog.com/2010/09/27/facebook-user-types/#comments</comments>
